This calculator is a versatile web-based tool designed with HTML, CSS, and JavaScript. 
It offers basic arithmetic operations (addition, subtraction, multiplication, and division)
alongside advanced functions like square root, square, and modulus. 
The calculator also supports parentheses for grouping operations, ensuring accurate calculations.
Its responsive design adapts to any screen size, with enhanced CSS styling providing a sleek, modern look. 
Buttons are intuitive, with visual feedback on hover and press, making it easy to use on both desktop and mobile devices. 
The JavaScript backend ensures smooth, real-time processing of all user inputs.
